-05-27T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11eee0a9aa66998ca1b1465aa85bc0b36d61e98","tid":256270,"uid":68505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"有肥仔千祈千祈唔好去夜店,試夜生活 一係你地叫佢stay係酒店 一係就一齊唔好去<br />\n同肥仔一齊去真係成班晒時間晒錢"},{"pid":"fd4aefdca2c5e0e2b3b8cb52bf3f318c556f7059","tid":256270,"uid":56203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:04:10.000Z","msg":"巿內景點(個人認為好流)半日行晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n七星潭睇日出+出海賞鯨一日<br />\n<br />\n可以包車行蘇花公路睇風景，去埋南方澳食海鮮，蘇澳浸冷泉<br />\n<br />\n夜巿，花蓮個東大門夜巿得個大字無野好食，建議你分一兩日去宜蘭，其中一晚去羅東夜巿"},{"pid":"6cde855d5df8df868c21fd0335c77f516b930df2","tid":256270,"uid":72881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巿內景點(個人認為好流)半日行晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n七星潭睇日出+出海賞鯨一日<br />\n<br />\n可以包車行蘇花公路睇風景，去埋南方澳食海鮮，蘇澳浸冷泉<br />\n<br />\n夜巿，花蓮個東大門夜巿得個大字無野好食，建議你分一兩日去宜蘭，其中一晚去羅東夜巿</blockquote><br />\nThx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20bb1b14ae9bb8e3908a7e069ca483f6d1d1346","tid":256270,"uid":52730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:27:51.000Z","msg":"樓主你幾時去？我30/5-2/6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想報個溯溪既one day tour 但佢最少要2條友 睇下有無機會一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea68cd4fa600007e719b3befd54fc1339064018","tid":256270,"uid":72881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你幾時去？我30/5-2/6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想報個溯溪既one day tour 但佢最少要2條友 睇下有無機會一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有冇telegram <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 私底下講<img src=\